        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nIs this tested in Ubuntu? does it works in those nodes?\n\nIf you use Ubuntu, you will need to set \"sign-artifacts: false\" since SIGUL is not supported on Ubuntu. \n\nPlease also be aware that staged/released artifacts will be unsigned. \n\nPerhaps you guys would like to leave stage and release jobs on Centos and only run tests on the merge or verify jobs in the Ubuntu nodes?",
